wikipedia_page.main: Daniel Williams (20 November 1924 – 3 February 2019) was an English football player and manager.

response: As of November 2018, 37 men have been appointed as a manager of Swindon Town Football Club, excluding caretaker managers. Danny Williams and Andy King are the only men to have been given the job on a permanent basis twice.
